{"data":[{"date":"13:39 20/08","title":"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd thua v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 pressing b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lu\u00f4n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 r\u00e1t khi tranh c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p n\u00ean ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Lee Young Jin \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \"b\u00ed k\u00edp\" m\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf trung tuy\u1ebfn trong khi ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 t\u1eeb t\u1ed1i 18/8, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 theo \u0111\u00fang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, ph\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic \u00a0Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 cao tay v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chinh ph\u1ee5c v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/24/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194893.html\">HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a  \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y song HLV Worrawoot Srimaka v\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u gi\u00fap \u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-len-tieng-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-cua-viet-nam-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194845.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/van-quyet-len-tieng-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-cua-viet-nam-truoc-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-len-tieng-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-cua-viet-nam-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194845.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5702","checkdouble":"194894"},{"date":"13:39 20/08","title":"Duy M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf ASIAD 2018. </h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 19/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o nh\u01b0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n khi tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/U23-VN-ha-Nhat-Ban-gay-soc-ASIAD-vi-sao-hot-boy-Duy-Manh-chua-u23-viet-nam-tao-dia-chan-39700513_138250136856113-1534738222-282-width660height440.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ee7 quan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00ed th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i sau l\u01b0ng k\u00ec t\u00edch \u1edf U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec3&nbsp;t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n&nbsp;l\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, v\u00ec v\u1eady to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t vui khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u00fd ngh\u0129a tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau ni\u1ec1m vui l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u1edf ASIAD&nbsp;c\u00f2n d\u00e0i, v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&nbsp;ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3&nbsp;t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;, Duy M\u1ea1nh chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i&nbsp;\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&nbsp;b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh,&nbsp;s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng hy sinh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00ec T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng&nbsp;mong mu\u1ed1n. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1 thay ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ai. Theo th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong ba b\u1ea3ng B, E, F. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Iran ho\u1eb7c Saudi Arabia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/24/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194893.html\">HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a  \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y song HLV Worrawoot Srimaka v\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u gi\u00fap \u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5701","checkdouble":"194895"},{"date":"14:43 20/08","title":"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/chan-thuong-cua-hung-dung-khong-can-phau-thuat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u00ec ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u qua 19/8, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/hung-dung-olympic-viet-nam_ukqp.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a t\u1edbi b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5p MRI t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n cho th\u1ea5y H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n c\u00e1i \u1edf b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean b\u00e0n m\u1ed5.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;Sau hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, BHL \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5p phim cho th\u1ea5y H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y \u0111\u1ed1t 2 ng\u00f3n c\u00e1i b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n, b\u00f3 b\u1ed9t v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n cho D\u0169ng. V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 6 tu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u00e1ng nay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chia hai nh\u00f3m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. M\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m s\u1ebd t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty Samsung, nh\u00f3m c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9, h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y. Chi\u1ec1u nay, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, F \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat-168-194895.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat-168-194895.html\">Duy M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/24/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-van-hy-vong-se-duoc-doi-dau-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194893.html\">HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a  \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y song HLV Worrawoot Srimaka v\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u gi\u00fap \u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5700","checkdouble":"194903"},{"date":"15:47 20/08","title":"T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Yuta Kamiya - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u qua 19/8, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Yuta Kamiya ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/A2-5776-1534743851.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Yuta Kamiya (tr\u00e1i) th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam qu\u00e1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb pha \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Obi, Yuta Kamiya tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng l\u1ed7i, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n cho Quang H\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m g\u1ecdn trong l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Yuta cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cL\u1ed7i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n do t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam qu\u00e1 nhanh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Kamiya s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u1eed l\u00fd sau \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00e1ng ra t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u00ean\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Yuta, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Miyoshi Yasuko c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ebb con n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng than v\u00e3n chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i sai l\u1ea7m khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Malaysia\", Miyoshi Yasuko cho hay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 6, 24/8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng A t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chan-thuong-cua-hung-dung-khong-can-phau-thuat-168-194903.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/chan-thuong-cua-hung-dung-khong-can-phau-thuat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chan-thuong-cua-hung-dung-khong-can-phau-thuat-168-194903.html\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt</span><br>\r\nTheo tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u00ec ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat-168-194895.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duy-manh-khong-chu-quan-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nguoi-nhat-168-194895.html\">Duy M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5699","checkdouble":"194906"},{"date":"16:10 20/08","title":"B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><h2>&nbsp;B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/5-JPG-9922-1534590659.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 do \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a BHL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh b\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00ec l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, b\u00e1c s\u0129 Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 do \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a BHL,</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ea3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Vi\u1ec7c Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 do \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a BHL th\u00f4i&rdquo;, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb b\u1edfi hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Do \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5t Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, b\u00e1c s\u0129 Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay ASIAD 2018 sau khi b\u1ecb g\u00e3y m\u1ed9t ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n \u1edf b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i. H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\">T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Yuta Kamiya - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5698","checkdouble":"194910"},{"date":"14:52 20/08","title":"Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, Real Madrid m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Courtois l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Navas \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i, song HLV Lopetegui v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-chi-200-trieu-euro-mua-sam-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lopetegui nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Cavani, Mauro Icardi hay Robert Lewandowski.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u HLV Lopetegui c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Vi\u1ec7c Mateo Kovaic \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f2n Luka Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV TBN mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn khi TTCN H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y Los Blancos s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real nh\u1eafm Edinson Cavani n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Julen Lopetegui \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi. C\u0169ng theo Don Balon, Real mu\u1ed1n mua Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG, Mauro\u00a0Icardi (Inter) v\u00e0 Rodrigo (Valencia).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Cavani</span> ho\u1eb7c Rodrigo, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Icardi, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Thiago c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thiago, Real s\u1ebd chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1eeb Lazio. Los Blancos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Los Blancos s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5697","checkdouble":"194897"},{"date":"14:39 20/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valencia vs Atletico Madrid 01h00 ng\u00e0y 21/8 (La Liga 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/nhan-dinh-valencia-vs-atletico-madrid-01h00-ngay-218-la-liga-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Valencia vs Atletico Madrid l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 21/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG T\u00e2y Ban Nha La Liga 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Valencia vs Atletico Madrid: 1-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Atletico Madrid b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch La Liga 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Mestalla c\u1ee7a Valencia. M\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, d\u00f9 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Diego Simeone v\u1eeba th\u1eafng Real Madrid c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, Atletico chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u1ee9 Castellon trong 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valencia vs Atletico Madrid 1h00 ng\u00e0y 218 La Liga 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valencia vs Atletico Madrid 1h00 ng\u00e0y 218 La Liga 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/180820_081959_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valencia vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Los Rojiblancos ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh tay, \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o 7 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi HLV Simeone, s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ed1t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid \u1edf Estonia, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. S\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Simeone c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Atletico trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u1edf Madrid \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c. C\u0169ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid, th\u1ef1c ra, c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ghi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb sai s\u00f3t trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng thay v\u00ec c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ri\u00eang, nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, Atletico v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u00f9ng l\u00ean, \u0111\u00f4i khi, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i theo ki\u1ec3u ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, \u00edt t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng Valencia th\u00ec c\u00f3. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Los Che gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League v\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Barcelona, Real Madrid hay Atletico, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 quan tr\u1ecdng cho vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n75 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Geoffrey Kondogbia t\u1eeb Inter Milan (25 tri\u1ec7u) v\u00e0 Kevin Gameiro (16) t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung 3 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1, trong khi tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi Michy Batshuayi t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u00e0 Denis Cheryshev \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, t\u1eeb Villarreal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Batshuayi v\u00e0 Gameiro n\u00ean h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 quen thu\u1ed9c d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Marcelino. Tuy ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Goncalo Guedes \u2013 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua t\u1eeb Paris Saint Germain, nh\u01b0ng Valencia v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Atletico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u01a1 l\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Madrid c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n, do \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nguy c\u01a1 s\u1ebd \u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n* L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n- Valencia: Francis Coquelin ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n- Atletico Madrid: Lucas Hernandez treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n-  Valencia kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Atletico trong 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i La  Liga (h\u00f2a 2, thua 5). L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Los Che c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0  th\u00e1ng 10/2014.<br>\r\n- Atletico gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Valencia g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n- Trong 2 th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Liga, Atletico \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u2013 th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1, thua 3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5696","checkdouble":"194899"},{"date":"15:27 20/08","title":"Sao Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Zidane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/dani-ceballos-phat-bieu-ve-zinedine-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zinedine Zidane. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Real Madrid d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ceballos kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Zidane tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDani Ceballos chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid t\u1eeb CLB \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra m\u00ecnh, Real Betis m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i La Liga trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Betis r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i U21 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 c\u00f9ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, n\u01a1i gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mang Ceballos v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Betis. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Zinedine Zidane, anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Ceballos ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real v\u1edbi 4 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zinedine Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zinedine Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/dani-ceballos-phat-bieu-ve-zinedine-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zinedine Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2018/19, Real b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Julen Lopetegui l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng thay cho Zinedine Zidane. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin h\u01a1n cho Dani Ceballos. Anh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Real gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH. Ceballos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i 71 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Luka Modric. Sau tr\u1eadn, Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zinedine Zidane. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho th\u1ea7y c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 Zidane, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y gi\u00fap t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\u201d, t\u1edd Marca tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Ceballos. \u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin sau c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ra s\u00e2n hi\u1ebfm hoi. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ra-quan-thang-loi-hlv-real-ca-ngoi-gareth-bale-180-194865.html\">Ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, HLV Real ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7-180-194863.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-real-madrid-vs-getafe-20-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194857.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5695","checkdouble":"194900"},{"date":"15:31 20/08","title":"Real Madrid \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/real-madrid-don-luong-cdv-thap-nhat-tu-ky-nguyen-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ea2nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u1edf Bernabeu khi Real Madrid \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y Cr7 gia nh\u1eadp.</h2><h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n La Liga 2018-19, Real Madrid cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe. Nh\u01b0ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008-09, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Cristiano Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rat nhieu ghe trong xuat hien o Bernabeu trong tran thang Getafe.\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gh\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Bernabeu trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Getafe.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/real-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gh\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Bernabeu trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Getafe.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3n 48.466 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 81.000 gh\u1ebf. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mallorca \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008-09.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy Cr7 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Juventus v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Ronaldo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Atletico v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-4. Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, khi Gareth Bale ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u0129nh \u1ea5n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid don luong CDV thap nhat tu ky nguyen Cristiano Ronaldo\" title=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/real-madrid-don-luong-cdv-thap-nhat-tu-ky-nguyen-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid \u0111\u00f3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Nacho cho r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo: &quot;Gareth Bale kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Bale, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Bale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vinh quang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec n\u1eefa&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Anh \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Anh \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi Real Madrid&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Real Madrid 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/dani-ceballos-phat-bieu-ve-zinedine-zidane-180-194900.html\">Sao Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Zidane</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/gareth-bale-noi-gi-sau-ngay-ra-quan-la-liga-cua-real-180-194887.html\">Gareth Bale n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga c\u1ee7a Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\">Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ra-quan-thang-loi-hlv-real-ca-ngoi-gareth-bale-180-194865.html\">Ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, HLV Real ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7-180-194863.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5694","checkdouble":"194902"},{"date":"17:04 20/08","title":"Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn anh v\u1edbi Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Liverpool h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Barca bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Firmino l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Firmino cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. T\u00f4i \u0111ang mang tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn lao t\u1eeb NHM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPremier League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thu h\u00fat sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cay \u0111\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nFirmino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf Liverpool hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho The Kop trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hoi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1ng cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 cho h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-2h-ngay-218-khang-dinh-suc-manh-172-194876.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crystal Palace vs Liverpool (2h ng\u00e0y 21/8): Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5693","checkdouble":"194914"},{"date":"17:18 20/08","title":"V\u00ec Chelsea, HLV Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea sau 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ng\u1eebng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chelsea ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Antonio Conte b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City t\u1ea1i Community Shield, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Sarri \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i The Blues kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018/19, Chelsea \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Huddersfield Town 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal 3-2 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Sarri t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH, c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Man City hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, quy \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Anh khi\u1ebfn cho Maurizio Sarri g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1edbn b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea7n gi\u1edd gi\u1ea3i lao v\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ebfu thu\u1ed1c\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00fat tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Arsenal, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u00e9p s\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 pressing, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i. Trong hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea-172-194881.html\">Morata: T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-mot-cau-thu-nao-cua-arsenal-du-suc-dung-trong-doi-hinh-chelsea-172-194868.html\">Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-kovacic-noi-gi-sau-man-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194861.html\">T\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-chia-se-ly-do-hut-chet-truoc-arsenal-172-194835.html\">Sao Chelsea chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do h\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5692","checkdouble":"194915"},{"date":"17:15 20/08","title":"Berbatov l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/berbatov-len-tieng-tran-an-cdv-mu-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dimitar Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V MU kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Brighton ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Amex. Nh\u01b0ng Berbatov kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Berbatov tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Berbatov tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/berbatov-len-tieng-tran-an-cdv-mu-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Berbatov l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V\u00a0MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t video \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang Instagram, Berbatov cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng coi n\u00e0o, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n thua. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. V\u1eady n\u00ean h\u00e3y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Man United s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Tottenham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 27/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Burnley v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 2/9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u1ed9t chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Antonio Valencia v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Spurs v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-thu-mu-xung-dang-bi-tram-khoi-doi-hinh-chinh-172-194913.html\">3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brighton-32-mu-172-194892.html\">2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5691","checkdouble":"194916"},{"date":"17:53 20/08","title":"L\u00fd do Liverpool s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c cho Alisson?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/ly-do-liverpool-su-dung-tui-bong-bau-duc-cho-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eebng s\u1ecf t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Chelsea, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Liverpool b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson t\u1eebng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Kepa Arrizabalaga. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1 m\u1eaft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/ly-do-liverpool-su-dung-tui-bong-bau-duc-cho-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 John Achterberg \u0111\u01b0a ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong l\u00fac m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111ang b\u00e1n t\u00edn b\u00e1n nghi v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\u201d, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi Loris Karius gia nh\u1eadp, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng l\u00fd g\u00ec Alisson kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i khu v\u1ef1c an to\u00e0n d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00ec Premier League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Alisson. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ngo\u00e0i Alisson, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-tiep-tuc-bung-no-chu-sadio-mane-172-194919.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace vs Liverpool: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9 Sadio Mane?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dortmund-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-origi-172-194891.html\">Dortmund s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-palace-lo-ngai-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-salah-172-194870.html\">HLV Palace lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-ve-cho-dung-bap-benh-o-liverpool-172-194860.html\">Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh \u1edf Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5690","checkdouble":"194917"}]}